org.apache.arrow.vector

Class VarCharVector

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.arrow.vector.BaseValueVector
      • org.apache.arrow.vector.BaseVariableWidthVector
        • org.apache.arrow.vector.VarCharVector
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Closeable, AutoCloseable, Iterable<ValueVector>, DensityAwareVector, FieldVector, ValueVector, VariableWidthVector, VectorDefinitionSetter

    public class VarCharVector
extends BaseVariableWidthVector
    VarCharVector implements a variable width vector of VARCHAR values which could be NULL. A validity buffer (bit vector) is maintained to track which elements in the vector are null.
